   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


Installing Maven
---------------- 
     sudo apt install Maven
     Maven home: /usr/share/maven

     
     issue in mave stage faced in pipeline
     1. Build failed becuse of mvn: command not found 
        
        solution : check the evn variable whether hoome path od java and maven defined correctly or not if still facing same issue 
                   creat a soft link like below 
                   cd /usr/bin
                   ln -s /opt/maven/bin/mvn mvn
                   try build again
                    
     2. pom.xml file not found
       check pom.xml is present or not if not present please create a pom.xml in /var/lib/jenkins/workspace/pom.xml

   

Install jenkins
---------------
   Sudo curl -fsSL https://pkg.jenkins.io/debian-stable/jenkins.io-2023.key | sudo tee /usr/share/keyrings/jenkins-keyring.asc > /dev/null  

   sudo echo deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/jenkins-keyring.asc]  https://pkg.jenkins.io/debian-stable binary/ | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/jenkins.list > /dev/null

   Sudo apt update

   apt install jenkins

   systemctl start jenkins

   systemctl enable jenkins


Installing sonarqube
--------------------
   sudo apt install unzip

   adduser soanrqube (adding this user because sonarqube will not run with root user)

   sudo su - sonarqube

   wget wget https://binaries.sonarsource.com/Distribution/sonarqube/sonarqube-9.4.0.54424.zip
    
   unzip "sonarqube-9.4.0.54424.zip"

   chmod -R 755 /home/sonarqube/sonarqube-9.4.0.54424
   
   chown -R sonarqube:sonarqube /home/sonarqube/sonarqube-9.4.0.54424

   cd /home/sonarqube/sonarqube-9.4.0.54424/bin/linux-x86-64/

   ./sonar.sh start

   copy the ip address of instance along with sonarqube port to access sonar web page https://<ipaddress>:9000


   pipeline steps:
   --------------
   # generate the token in sonarqube to confiure with jenkins
   #go to soanrqube-my account-security here give token name  and copy the token 
   soanrqube credentials need to set in manage jenkins-credentials-system-global credentials
   select type as secret text
   give (username - jenkins ; text-  paste generated token)
   jenkins - 8c25f32817e133b2631abc91e138cd662bc68e05


install Docker
--------------

   sudo apt update

   sudo apt install docker.io

   sudo su -

      providing the permissions to jenkins user and docker user to docker deamon.

      usermod -aG docker jenkins
      usermod -aG docker ubuntu
      systemctl restart docker

      Restart jennkins after installing any tool or plugin in jenkins server.




   